An Amiga developer friend, John Foust, late of the net, gave this to 
me to post.

This is the IBM to Amiga text filter.  It translates stdin to the hex 
stream that AmigaDOS "READ" needs, expanding TABs to spaces, ignoring 
CR, and passing LF.

Rick Wirch


